---
title: Cheddar & Apple Grilled Cheese Sandos with Cranberry-Dijon Jam
description: Sure, a classic white bread and American grilled cheese hits the spot every now and then, but try one bite of this 15-minute sweet and savory lunch idea, and you may never quite be satisfied with the old standby again. Sourdough slices are swiped with sweet and tangy cranberry-Dijon jam, then layered with cheddar and mild Monterey Jack cheeses and crisp apple slices. They’re griddled in butter until perfectly golden brown and melty. Flip onto your plate, and boom—lunch, elevated!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64a4fab73223226bfd2b8b2b-a589e79e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64a4fab73223226bfd2b8b2b.pdf
author: Sara Heilman
servings: 2
time required: 15 minutes
